menu_buildjob
[TITLE]The Manual:  Building Tasks[/TITLE]
[C:7:0:1]How to Get Here[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Press [IKEY:D_BUILDJOB] from the main view.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Description[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Here you can set up tasks at buildings, create rooms and set other building properties.  You can also designate buildings for destruction here.
[B][B]
[C:7:0:1]Standard Menu[C:7:0:0]
[B]
Most buildings, including workshops, use a standard menu.  Here you can create tasks, set their priority, cancel them,
or set them to repeat.  Any healthy unoccupied dwarf with the proper professions will perform these tasks.
[B]
[LINK:data/help/menu_professions]Setting Professions[/LINK]
[B][B]
